AGI - The instructor judge of Palma de Mallorca ordered the temporary detention of the four tourists arrested that a young woman accused her of sexually assaulting her in a Playa de Palma apartment where she had gone to have a consensual relationship with one of them. According to what has announced today the command of the national police of the Balearics, the facts have happened between 2.00 and 6.30 on Sunday and the four arrested are of Italian nationality.
&nbsp;
The victim met one of the tourists at a nightclub on the Paseo Maritimo of the capital of the Balearics, liked and agreed to move to the apartment where the young man stayed in Playa de Palma. In this lodging, which the man shared with three friends, the young woman and he had consensual sexual intercourse, but then the other guests entered the room and allegedly raped her holding her firm and forcing her. The complainant left the tourist facility after taking the passport of one of the attackers and went with him to a police station where he reported the incident.
&nbsp;
In accordance with the protocol for cases of sexual violence, the national police transferred the victim to a medical center. On the basis of the testimony of the young woman, the investigators collected information, located the accommodation of the accused and proceeded to their arrest before they left the island, which they planned to do on Sunday. The four tourists were brought to court this morning as alleged authors of a crime of sexual violence, and the court in turn ordered custody without bail.

